    "description": "Discipline: Qinggong\nSkill: Leg Strike\nType: Normal\nQi: 2\n\nYou leap great distance toward a foe unleashing a high kick and using the target to spring back upon another enemy. On a Success you can leap up to 10 feet per Rank of Qinggong to kick your opponent, doing Muscle +1d10 Damage. You can then leap another 10 feet per Rank of Qinggong against another foe (also doing Muscle +1d10 Damage). Use your original roll for both attacks. Cathartic: When used Cathartically you can make an additional number of leaping kick attacks equal to your Rank in Qi (again, use the same roll for all of them).",
